<br>
For example for best feudal japan I'd say Hiroaki Samura.  He has 3 different styles of drawing:  normal with tones etc., hatched pen work like in Lodoss War (but cleaner), and the pencil drawings....*drools*.  <br>
<br>
Hmm, Romance/ light comedy I'd say Yuu Watase.  Lessee...for out and out funniest I'd say the character designers of Dragon Half or Excel Saga.  <br>
<br>
On the other end of the spectrum (occult/gory/spooky)  I'd say the designers of Miyu or Blood Reign:  Curse of the Yoma.<br>
<br>
<br>
And yet on the other end of the spectrum (insane american) I'd say J. Vasquez for best black and white comic (Johnny, Squee, Zim)<br>
<br>
Maybe we at Polykarbon BBS should hold some kind of Academy Awards?  (Best Backgrounds, use of tones, genres, etc...) <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=1239.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=1239.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=1239.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=1239.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1239.topic&index=48><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.emailToFriend?topicID=1239.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.threadControl?topicID=1239.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1239.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1239.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub25.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr>